sentences: Conor Paul Maynard (born 21 November 1992) is an English singer, songwriter, actor and YouTuber.
Born and raised in Brighton, he signed a recording contract with Warner Music Group in 2011.
Maynard rose to fame in 2012 when he was nominated for, and subsequently won, MTV's Brand New for 2012 award.
